              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="swiper-slide">
            <div class="application-slider__slide-text">
              <span class="label">APPLICATION</span>
              <p>
                02 ) Use your fingertips to gently massage the serum into the scalp for 30â€“60 seconds to help with
                absorption and stimulate circulation.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="swiper-slide">
            <div class="application-slider__slide-text">
              <span class="label">APPLICATION</span>
              <p>
                03 ) Do not rinse. Let the formula absorb fully overnight for best results. Use once daily, preferably
                in the evening for consistent results.
              </p>
            </div>
